### Create hybrid link.
{{% example csharp %}}
```csharp
using Pulumi;
using AzureNextGen = Pulumi.AzureNextGen;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var hybridLink = new AzureNextGen.Sql.V20200801Preview.HybridLink("hybridLink", new AzureNextGen.Sql.V20200801Preview.HybridLinkArgs
        {
            DistributedAvailabilityGroupName = "dag",
            ManagedInstanceName = "testcl",
            PrimaryAvailabilityGroupName = "BoxLocalAg1",
            ResourceGroupName = "testrg",
            SecondaryAvailabilityGroupName = "testcl",
            SourceEndpoint = "TCP://SERVER:7022",
            TargetDatabase = "testdb",
        });
    }

}

```
